snippet.title: Kerbal Space Program 2 Early Access Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist KSP 2:

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/954850/Kerbal_Space_Program_2/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=o_social&utm_campaign=kspearlyaccess&utm_term=gameplaytrailer
Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/kerbal-space-program-2
Direct Download: https://store.privatedivision.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2

Early Access launch is just one week away!
Kerbal Space Program 2 will be releasing in Early Access on February 24th, 2023, for an introductory price of $49.99. The game will be available on PC only during Early Access, on the KSP website, Steam, and Epic Games Store.
Big thanks to Simple Films for helping us create this trailer, and Zach Heyde for the music!

Don’t miss another KSP launch!
